<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, May 6 (Xinhua) -- The Tunis Stock Exchange index closed at
578.64 points on Thursday, up 0.64 percent from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A daily bulletin of the bourse said 35,002 shares changed hands
in 232 deals, and the turnover was 677,129 dinars (615,571
U.S. dollars). 
</P>
