Africa and economic and political challenges facing the continent
in addition to efforts exerted to reach peaceful solutions to
disputes among several African countries.
</P>
<P>
Egypt is keen on helping seek solution to the border disputes
between Eritrea and Ethiopia, the armed conflicts in the
Democratic Republic of Congo (DR Congo) and disputes between DR
Congo, on the one hand, and Uganda and Rwanda, on the other.
