24.
</P>
<P>
The market's turnover was 11.366 billion HK dollars (1.457
billion U.S. dollars), 1.888 billion HK dollars (242 million U.S.
dollars) less than Thursday's 13.254 billion HK dollars (1.699
billion U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
