496.46 and ended the morning session 409.36 points lower at 13,160.
88.
</P>
<P>
For the whole trading week, Hong Kong share prices lost 335.77
points. Transactions remained above the 13,000-point level the
whole week except Friday.
</P>
<P>
Analysts say the fall is no surprise and there is no reason to
panic.
</P>
<P>
Brokers predicted that this downward correction would continue
next week. 
