fiercely airstrikes on Yugoslavia which leave people dead and
injured everyday.
</P>
<P>
He pointed out that Russia could not solve the problem solely,
but will make joint efforts with the international community as
soon as possible.
</P>
<P>
On Thursday, foreign ministers from the G8 -- made up of the
biggest western industrial powers plus Russia -- agreed on a seven-
point plan to be endorsed by the U.N. Security Council that calls
for a deployment of "effective international civil and security
presence" in Kosovo.
</P>
<P>
