<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, May 7 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong fell
28 HK dollars to close at 2,632 HK dollars a tael on Friday,
according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers in Hong
Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 285.03 U.S. dollars a troy
ounce, or 3.02 U.S. dollars down from the previous close at
Friday's exchange rate of one U.S. dollar against 7.7512 HK
dollars. 
</P>
