<HEADLINE> Shenzhen Stock Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 7 (Xinhua) -- The Component Stock Index on the
Shenzhen Stock Exchange closed at 2,766.20 points today, down 45.
16 points from the previous session, according to the Guangfa
Securities Co. Ltd.
